223    /**
224    * A general class for plotting data in the form of (x, y) pairs. This plot can
225    * use data from any class that implements the {@link XYDataset} interface.
226    * <P>
227    * <code>XYPlot</code> makes use of an {@link XYItemRenderer} to draw each point
228    * on the plot. By using different renderers, various chart types can be
229    * produced.
230    * <p>
231    * The {@link org.jfree.chart.ChartFactory} class contains static methods for
232    * creating pre-configured charts.
233    */
